# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3D viewer — recorded trajectories
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Real rollouts can be large; keep them local. The committed demo (generated by
# `python viz/make_demo_trajectory.py`) is the exception so the viewer ships
# working out of the box. Force-add your own with `git add -f` if you want one.
viz/web/trajectories/*.json
!viz/web/trajectories/demo_trajectory.json

